Inner Engineering Total (4 day program)*
 

We are happy to announce that, after 4 years Isha Australia is re-introducing the live Inner Engineering program designed by Sadhguru and conducted by a trained teacher. Previously offered as a 7-day course, it is now offered as a 4-day weekend programme with brand new content.


Perth: 16 - 19 Mar (Early bird offer available for a limited time!)

Venue : City of Melville Main Hall, 10 Almondbury Rd, Booragoon, WA [MAP]

Brisbane: 23 - 26 Mar (Early bird offer available for a limited time!)

Venue : Little Flower Church Hall, 80 Turner Rd, Kedron [MAP]

Melbourne: 30 Mar - 02 Apr (Early bird offer available for a limited time!)

Venue : Brunswick Town Hall, Brunswick [MAP]

Session Timings:

Thursday & Friday: 6 pm - 9:15 pm
Saturday: 8 am - 6 pm
Sunday: 7 am - 6 pm


* No Pre-Requisite needed
